Package org.forgerock.openam.sso.providers.stateless

Class StatelessSession

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iplanet.dpro.session.Session
      • org.forgerock.openam.sso.providers.stateless.StatelessSession
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Blacklistable, AMSession
    public class StatelessSession
extends Session
    The StatelessSession class represents a stateless session. It is a simple overridden version of Session which allows for the addition of extra methods, or overriding of inherited ones.
